Antagony smiled at Vlad when he replied. "I'm Antigany," she said, 
stretching out her hand. "Its nice to meet you. Have you been here long?"

She already knew the answer thanks to her limited ability to see into the 
future, but that future still needed to happen, so she asked the question.
